# Accessing Unit Level Resources
![](https://images.code.org/d66347b3b5bd21066f83200ac3244803-image-1742933817353.16.51 PM.png)
#### 1. From the Unit Overview page, navigate to your unit of choice. 
#### 2. Click on "Go to Unit" 

![](https://images.code.org/ebeb3ec12d2ffe66ad776bd91ed056fd-image-1742933858347.17.34 PM.png)

#### 3. Click on "Teacher Resources"
#### 4. Select your resource 
